      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">The System Prompt is Simpler Than You Think</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">People overcomplicate system prompts. They write novels, embed entire knowledge bases, and try to anticipate every edge case. The best system prompts are short, clear, and point to external context.</p>
